videos.description: Jarred Vanderbilt blocks Mustapha Heron's shot then makes a nice pass to Quade Green for the layup.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's block leads to bucket for Kentucky

videos.description: Bryce Brown makes a nice in and out dribble then drills the transition 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Brown's sick handle leads to bucket

videos.description: The Auburn Tigers' football team appeared with the cheerleaders at halftime in a routine and seemed to be in unison with them.
videos.headline: Tigers' football team perfroms at halftime

videos.description: Wenyen Gabriel drives baseline and throws down a mean two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Gabriel punishes the rim on dunk

videos.description: Anfrnee McLemore throws down two alley-oops with authority.
videos.headline: Tigers' McLemore has some serious hops

videos.description: No. 10 Auburn outlasts Kentucky at home behind 18 points each from Bryce Brown and Jared Harper.
